## Bawishikulu balemucinkulako nokuti bashelefye ne myaka inoono ukuti bakaleke imilimo pamukoti panuma yakupoka penshoni nokuyaikala ku mushi mukusunga bawishi ba Fungamwango ilyo umwana wabo Shi-Mumamba Solo akalabatangaata
